Class EnsembleCl<T>

java.lang.Object
ensemble.EnsembleCl<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Ensemble<T>
public class EnsembleCl<T> extends Object implements Ensemble<T>
The EnsembleCl class represents a generic set of elements of type T using a Set to store elements.
